this function should be used for updating wallet of a customer
note*:this function updates wallet of a customer and also creates a log on wallet too,so strictly follow the below payload structure for integration
case 1 :if money is credtied to customer
payload:{
    "cus_id": "62d96b1e08906e32b35e793b",
    "credit":50
}

case 2: if money is debited from customer
payload:{
    "cus_id": "62d96b1e08906e32b35e793b",
    "debit": 500
}

This Api's Model Has Been Changed on 05-07-22
the changes to this api from today is the following
previous payload was:
{
     "expenseType": "miscallaneous",
    "amount": 5000,
    "date": "2022-07-05",
    "paidBy": "cash",
    "branchId": "FAN2",
}

new payload:
{
   "expenseType": "miscallaneous",
    "amount": 5000,
    "date": "2022-07-05",
    "paidBy": "cash",
    "branchId": "FAN2",
    "creditAmount": 500,
    "lastPaidAmount": 200,
    "lastPaidDate": "2022-07-05",
    "paymentMethod": {
        "type": "cash",
        "amount": 200
    } 
}
*note: in the new payload the paymentMethod field is strictly dynamic,the possible values so far is mentioned below:
{
    paymentMethod:{
        "type": "cash",
        "amount": 200
    },
    paymentMethod:{
        "type":"Card",
        "amount":200,
        "cardType":"Visa",
        "cardNo":"******",
        "cvv":***
    },
    paymentMethod:{
        "type":"Upi",
        "upiId":"*****",
        "amount":200
    }
}

